## Overview
The Superhero Training Academy is an interactive game designed to train superheroes in various skills needed to save the day! The game features modular levels, and players can choose between English and Kannada language support.

## Game Framework Structure

### 1. Main Game Loop
```python
class Game:
    def __init__(self):
        self.language = "English"
        self.levels = []
        self.current_level = 0

    def load_language(self, lang):
        if lang in ["English", "Kannada"]:
            self.language = lang
        else:
            print("Language not supported.")

    def start_game(self):
        print(self.translations[self.language]['welcome'])
        self.current_level = 0
        self.levels[self.current_level].start()

    def next_level(self):
        self.current_level += 1
        if self.current_level < len(self.levels):
            self.levels[self.current_level].start()
        else:
            print(self.translations[self.language]['end_game'])
```

